{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_123","type":"agent_message","text":"Completed the study end to end. The main deliverables are [REPORT.md](/workspaces/sycophancy-lang-resources-d777-codex/REPORT.md), [README.md](/workspaces/sycophancy-lang-resources-d777-codex/README.md), [planning.md](/workspaces/sycophancy-lang-resources-d777-codex/planning.md), and the pipeline in [src/run_full_study.py](/workspaces/sycophancy-lang-resources-d777-codex/src/run_full_study.py).\n\nThe key result is mixed: lower-resource languages clearly reduced factual QA accuracy, but they did not increase measured BullshitBench capitulation in this setup. On `gpt-4.1-mini`, MKQA final accuracy dropped from `0.625` in high-resource languages to `0.425` in low-resource languages; on `Qwen/Qwen2.5-3B-Instruct`, it dropped from `0.275` to `0.050`. But BullshitBench capitulation moved the other way: `gpt-4.1-mini` was `5.4%` high-resource vs `2.0%` low-resource, and Qwen was `1.5%` vs `0.5%`. The strongest intervention result was local steering on Qwen: BullshitBench final rejection rose from `69.3%` base to `94.7%` steered, with measured capitulation falling to `0%`.\n\nArtifacts are in [results/analysis/metrics_summary.csv](/workspaces/sycophancy-lang-resources-d777-codex/results/analysis/metrics_summary.csv), [results/mechanistic/local_mechanistic_summary.json](/workspaces/sycophancy-lang-resources-d777-codex/results/mechanistic/local_mechanistic_summary.json), and the figures in [figures/bullshitbench_capitulation_by_language.png](/workspaces/sycophancy-lang-resources-d777-codex/figures/bullshitbench_capitulation_by_language.png), [figures/mkqa_final_accuracy_by_language.png](/workspaces/sycophancy-lang-resources-d777-codex/figures/mkqa_final_accuracy_by_language.png), [figures/mechanistic_layer_auc.png](/workspaces/sycophancy-lang-resources-d777-codex/figures/mechanistic_layer_auc.png), and [figures/challenge_direction_norms.png](/workspaces/sycophancy-lang-resources-d777-codex/figures/challenge_direction_norms.png). Reproduction is `source .venv/bin/activate && python src/run_full_study.py`."}}
